    <h1>Increase/decrease the number of licenses</h1>

    <p>If you have increased/decreased your licence:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Find the original license in <a href="../../../list-of-windows/alvao-asset-management-console/software/license-registry">License Audit</a> and from the local menu use <a href="../../../list-of-windows/alvao-asset-management-console/software/license-registry/edit/edit-license">Edit</a>.
        </li>
        <li>On the tab <a href="../../../list-of-windows/alvao-asset-management-console/software/license-registry/edit/edit-license/general">General</a> edit the number in the <b>Number</b> field to match the new status.</li>
        <li>Go to the <a href="../../../list-of-windows/alvao-asset-management-console/software/license-registry/edit/edit-license/documents">Documents</a> tab and add a link to the invoice that documents the purchase.</li>
        <li>Save your changes using the <b>OK</b> button.</li>
    </ul>

</asp:Content>






